When an emergency strikes, you need help and need that help fast, before it is too late to do anything about it. A financial emergency also has similar requirements, wherein, you need immediate funds to meet the urgent requirement that has cropped up. Any individual would first look at the easiest options available to him, when looking for immediate financial assistance. One such option may be asking a friend or family member for a loan. However, firstly, it might be embarrassing to divulge your financial status to a known person. And secondly, the individual you approach for help may not have the necessary funds at his disposal, thus, be unable to help you out financially. A much safer option would be to apply for a financial loan that can provide you with instant cash to support any financial need in between two consecutive paydays. In short, apply for a loan that provides you ready cash till your next payday, when such a loan can be repaid instantly. However, you may have apprehensions about approaching any financial lender, as any traditional loan would take a fair amount of paperwork for verification and processing of the loan, before you can actually get the loan approval and then the cash. When time, however, is a crucial factor, then you can avoid waiting in long lines and going through the process of lengthy paperwork for loan approval by making the smart choice of applying for the no paperwork payday loans.

